  <brief_title>Safety and Efficacy of BAY1192631 in Japanese Patients With Methicillin-resistant Staphylococcus Aureus (MRSA) Infections</brief_title>
  <official_title>A Prospective, Randomized, Open-label, Active-controlled, Multicenter Study to Evaluate the Efficacy and Safety of BAY 1192631 in Japanese Patients With MRSA Infections (Skin and Soft Tissue Infection [SSTI] and SSTI-related Bacteremia)</official_title>
