  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      The aim of this study is to see the safety and efficacy of BAY1192631 when it is used for the
      treatment of skin and soft tissue infections (SSTI) or SSTI-related bacteremia.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
